Notes: Sen. Gretchen Hoffman, R-Vergas, is running for the 7th congressional district seat. She has not been clear whether this means she will not try to return to the Legislature should her congressional ambitions not come to fruition. Hoffman, who was paired with Sen. Bill Ingebrigtsen, R-Alexandria, in the new political maps, has endorsed him in his run for the 8th district Senate seat.
